General.Name: PowerUp Acquisition Corp. Warrant
General.Description: PowerUp Acquisition Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to identify and acquire a business within the interactive media, digital media, sports, entertainment, and/or leisure areas. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
